This paper proposes a new online learning scheme that improves upon an existing algorithm and achieves better predictive accuracy while being computationally efficient. The paper focuses on machine learning and classification tasks, which are typically covered in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
